{"tid":859852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹尿尿意外跌入溝　友人救援同受困 估地方","createTime":"2018-10-13T01:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T03:20:16.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b92805e6e132d6f2c0902832fbd74888dd0113d","tid":859852,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"位於新北市蘆洲區的微風運河公園，是許多民眾散步休閒的首選，但今晨5時許，警消獲報有2民眾跌落高約5公尺的排水溝內，趕緊前往救援，警消將2人救起後才得知，原來是其中1女性欲「小號」卻不慎跌落，另名女性搶救不成也跌落，所幸2人皆無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查，石女與高女（皆約20歲）相約到微風運河散步，石女突然尿急，就近找了排水溝解決，卻不慎掉落，高女著急爬下去救她卻也跌落，救援失敗的高女就在排水溝打119並陪伴石女。<br />\n20分鐘後，警消終於在排水溝發現2人，放下雙節梯讓2人爬上平地，石女右腳扭傷、高女左手擦傷，2人送醫後皆無大礙。警消提醒，若遇緊急狀況或是生理不適時，還是要衡量當下環境，千萬別大意忽略周遭環境的不可測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181013/1446778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181013%2F1446778&d=QvySEdzGX266GlvRhfVdUTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1e39cb60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181013%2F1446778&h=a68337ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181013/1446778</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181013/640_58cbd862f47e2c6690a817c1dc50f23c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181013%2F640_58cbd862f47e2c6690a817c1dc50f23c.jpg&h=82de471a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181013/640_cdc5500d05d8b2e4d8ec32bb3ac5b7da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181013%2F640_cdc5500d05d8b2e4d8ec32bb3ac5b7da.jpg&h=2902f663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181013/640_9c79c3ac3962ed7b92f2709baf827b2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181013%2F640_9c79c3ac3962ed7b92f2709baf827b2c.jpg&h=3a601d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181013/640_9f9646430e2a11c559c744762b2f6393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181013%2F640_9f9646430e2a11c559c744762b2f6393.jpg&h=f4d68be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c33016e1b3a52516de2c4440038a00b19535d2c","tid":859852,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ee89a11024a4bc2708bb322f765e375143611a1","tid":859852,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:22:40.000Z","msg":"新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77af703d05389a06bc8c5a41e337a1cfcfa5e8f4","tid":859852,"uid":78500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"內文係2個女人,但張相係一男一女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce64b2259648375d167eee7d1a132519d026fd5f","tid":859852,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a6b4f3f1f6ae56aafc8f1474742f20bf441339d","tid":859852,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:30:01.000Z","msg":"台妹一跌落渠，就連部單車都失去"},{"pid":"c7ec90a3f114a886699ee805dfbbecee95ea9a68","tid":859852,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:31:29.000Z","msg":"另一個係TB?"},{"pid":"bd177ec67dc2ad2a8f7d32696f2c357420f58024","tid":859852,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce64b2259648375d167eee7d1a132519d026fd5f","tid":859852,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77af703d05389a06bc8c5a41e337a1cfcfa5e8f4","tid":859852,"uid":78500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cite